Value interface (\S+)
Value description (.*)
Value mac ([0-9A-Fa-f:\.-]+)
Value ip (\d+\.\d+\.\d+\.\d+\/\d+)

Start
  ^${interface}\s+current\s+state.*$$ -> Record
  ^\s*Description:\s*${description}\s*$$ -> Record
  ^\s*Hardware\s+address\s+is\s+${mac}.*$$ -> Record
  ^\s*Internet\s+Address\s+is\s+${ip}.*$$ -> Record

